Hazel Terry https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hazel_Terry 0 Hazel Terry (born Hazel M. Neilson-Terry; 23 January 1918 – 12 October 1974) was an English actress. A member of the theatrical dynasty the Terry family she had a successful stage career, and also made some cinema films. Among her roles was Ophelia in Hamlet opposite her cousin John Gielgud.
